                <p>It’s also important to us that you are committed to equalities and the environment. We’ll want to know about your equalities policy and your environmental policy if we’re interested in your idea.</p>

                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://www.biglotteryfund.org.uk/about-big/our-approach/equalities">Our equality principles</a></li>
